      <title>萨默斯：政客介入美联储是“愚人游戏”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/summers-fool-s-game-for-politicians-to-get-involved-with-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前财政部长、《华尔街周刊》撰稿人劳伦斯·萨默斯警告称，政客和总统不应参与美联储的货币政策决策。他还表示，日本央行最近对市场波动的反应“会给其风格扣分”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/summers-fool-s-game-for-politicians-to-get-involved-with-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:58:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
